**Repository**: [cto4ai/claude-skills](https://github.com/cto4ai/claude-skills)

**What it does**:
- Create, read, update documentation files in this repository
- Find and search documents
- Organize documentation structure
- Commit changes to GitHub

**How to use**:
- **Internal distribution**: Install from claude-skills repo (current)
- **Future**: Claude.ai Skills Marketplace

**Example**:
```
